SUMMARY:Improv Happy Hour
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Improv Happy Hour\, where comedy is unscripted\, unpredictable\, and unbelievably fun! From movie mashups to literary spoofs and bold\, experimental comedy\, our quick-thinking performers turn your suggestions into hilarious scenes on the spot. \n\n\nThis family-friendly show at the iconic Gum Wall in Pike Place Market guarantees a night of laughter\, surprises\, and improv magic you won’t forget. Bring your wildest ideas\, your loudest laughs\, and get ready for a one-of-a-kind comedy experience—because at Improv Happy Hour\, anything can happen (and usually does)!
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-happy-hour/2026-04-18/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/HappyHour.jpg
END:VEVENT
