DESCRIPTION:Step into a world where your memories spark the unexpected\, your objects tell untold stories\, and your life becomes art in motion. With a swirl of spontaneous theater\, hand-typed poetry\, and the soulful sounds of live musicians\, each night unfolds like a dream—unrepeatable\, electric\, and uniquely yours. One moment\, you’re laughing at a scene born from a trinket in your pocket; the next\, a poem crafted just for you finds its way into your hands. This is poetry in motion. This is music in the moment. This is theater made from the fabric of your life. Come laugh. Come cry. Come as you are. \n✨ THIS IS FOR YOU! ✨ \nDon’t miss this once-in-a-lifetime fusion of words\, sound\, and improvisation. April is the month of poetry—come celebrate the magic!
