UID:10011448-1776711600-1776718800@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:IMPROV 100 ISSAQUAH - Intro to Improv: Say Yes!\, SPRING '26
DESCRIPTION:Discover improv in Issaquah. Build confidence\, meet new people\, and learn to create stories through fun\, supportive games and scene work.\n\n\n\nLooking for a fun\, fresh way to connect with others\, spark creativity\, and step out of the everyday routine? Welcome to Intro to Improv at Unexpected Productions Improv School Eastside in Issaquah. Whether you are a working professional hoping to improve communication\, a creative soul searching for a new outlet\, or someone simply wanting more laughter and community in your week\, this class is the perfect place to begin. \nIn this beginner-friendly course\, you will learn the foundational skills of improvisation: active listening\, collaboration\, spontaneity\, and using your own life experiences to create honest\, engaging scenes and stories. Improv is not about being funny\, it is about being present\, supportive\, and open. And yes\, along the way\, you will laugh more than you have in ages. \nOur community values connection and growth\, and this class is built on those principles. You will work in a supportive group where the guiding philosophy is simple: When your scene partner looks good\, you look good. Together\, we build trust\, confidence\, and creativity\, one scene at a time. \n\nUnder the guidance of our experienced faculty\, you will learn to:\nBe a better listener\nConquer fears and build confidence\nSpark creativity\nMeet new people and make real connections\nBecome a better problem solver\nSay yes more in your life\nStep out of your comfort zone\nImprove public speaking\nFail easier (and laugh about it)\nDiscover more about yourself\nHave an absolute blast\n\nThis class includes lots of laughter\, lots of stage time\, and zero pressure. Every student begins here. No experience needed. Just bring curiosity and a willingness to try something new. \nUnexpected Productions Improv School is thrilled to bring our newest Eastside improv classes to Issaquah\, serving the communities of the Sammamish Plateau\, East Renton\, Bellevue\, Snoqualmie Valley\, and beyond. \nClass Details\nDates: Six (8) Monday classes \nTime: 7:00pm to 9:00pm \nLocation: Improv School Eastside Issaquah \n1315 NW Mall Street\, Suite 4 Issaquah\, WA 98027 (next to the Gaslamp Bar & Grill) \nMaximum students: 16 \nAges: 18 plus \nCost: $320 \nPrerequisite: None \nNote: Attendance at the first session is mandatory\, as it sets the tone and foundation for the entire quarter. If you know you will miss the first class\, please register for a future session.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/intro-to-improv-eastside-issaquah-mondays/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\, 1315 NW Mall Street\, Suite 4\, Issaquah\, WA\, 98108\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/IMG_3519-scaled.jpg
